# Build Standards - MoonProject

## 1. Define Symbols

| Symbol | Mục đích | Môi trường |
|--------|----------|------------|
| `DEV_LOGS` | Enable debug logging | Dev build |
| `STAGING` | Staging server endpoints | Staging |
| `PROD` | Production config | Release |
| `ENABLE_CHEATS` | Cheat menu (CheatButton) | Dev only |

### Quy tắc:
- Debug.Log trong production: wrap trong `#if DEV_LOGS`
- Cheat features: wrap trong `#if ENABLE_CHEATS`
- KHÔNG dùng `Debug.Log` trực tiếp trong production code mới

## 2. Build Pipeline

### Pre-build checklist
- [ ] Tất cả scenes trong Build Settings
- [ ] Addressables build update
- [ ] Localization tables complete
- [ ] Define symbols đúng cho target environment
- [ ] Version number updated (SemVer)

### Android
| Setting | Dev | Release |
|---------|-----|---------|
| IL2CPP | OFF (Mono) | ON |
| Minify | OFF | Proguard/R8 |
| Split APKs | OFF | ON (ABB) |
| Debug symbols | Full | Upload to Play Console |

### iOS
| Setting | Dev | Release |
|---------|-----|---------|
| IL2CPP | ON | ON |
| Bitcode | OFF | OFF (deprecated) |
| Strip Engine Code | OFF | ON |

## 3. Version

- Format: `MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH` (SemVer)
- `bundleVersionCode` (Android) / `buildNumber` (iOS): auto-increment
- Tag git: `v{version}` cho mỗi release

## 4. CI Pipeline (khuyến nghị)

```
Commit → Lint/Format Check → Unit Tests → Addressables Build 
  → Dev Build (Android) → Smoke Test → Release Build
```

### Bước tối thiểu:
1. **Format check**: Verify code style
2. **Unit tests**: `Assets/Tests/EditMode/`
3. **Build**: Dev APK cho mỗi PR
4. **Size report**: So sánh build size với previous

## 5. Addressables

- Rebuild Addressables trước mỗi build
- Group strategy: Default Local, Remote (maps, large assets)
- Content update: sử dụng `Check for Content Update Restrictions`

---

### Ví dụ ĐÚNG

```csharp
public void LogGameEvent(string eventName)
{
#if DEV_LOGS
    Debug.Log($"[Analytics] Event: {eventName}");
#endif
    FirebaseAnalytics.LogEvent(eventName);
}
```

### Ví dụ SAI

```csharp
public void LogGameEvent(string eventName)
{
    Debug.Log($"[Analytics] Event: {eventName}"); // Log trong production
    FirebaseAnalytics.LogEvent(eventName);
}
```
